{DIALOGUE}: Well, freshman, looks like you're going to make it after all.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: GEORGE
{DIALOGUE}: Yep.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sam sees Harry and leaves George in the middle of a gesture.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SAM
{META_DATA}: (to Harry)
{DIALOGUE}: Harry!
{DIALOGUE}: You're the guy I want to see.
{DIALOGUE}: Coach has heard all about you.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HARRY
