{CHARACTER_NAME}: HARRY
{DIALOGUE}: Well, I gotta make some dough first.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SAM
{DIALOGUE}: Well, you better make it fast.
{DIALOGUE}: We need great ends like you – not broken down old guys like this one.
