{CHARACTER_NAME}: GEORGE
{DIALOGUE}: And I told Harry I thought I'd be bored to death.
{DIALOGUE}: You should have seen the commotion in that locker room.
{DIALOGUE}: I had to knock down three people to get this stuff we're wearing here.
{DIALOGUE}: Here, let me hold that old wet dress of yours.
