{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSEUP – GEORGE AND CLARENCE
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: George indicates his bad ear.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: GEORGE
{DIALOGUE}: Say something else in that ear.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: CLARENCE
{META_DATA}: (bending down)
{DIALOGUE}: Sure.
{DIALOGUE}: You can hear out of it.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: GEORGE
