{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. NICK'S BAR – NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE SHOT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: George and Clarence lying in the snow.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: George has a strange, puzzled look on his face.
