{CHARACTER_NAME}: GEORGE
{META_DATA}: (furious)
{DIALOGUE}: Now shut up!
{DIALOGUE}: Cut it out!
{DIALOGUE}: You're... you're... you're crazy!
{DIALOGUE}: That's what I think... you're screwy, and you're driving me crazy, too!
{DIALOGUE}: I'm seeing things.
{DIALOGUE}: I'm going home and see my wife and family.
{DIALOGUE}: Do you understand that?
{DIALOGUE}: And I'm going home alone!
